IN THE UNITED STATES, NIKE HAS FIVE SIGNIFICANT DISTRIBUTION CENTERS LOCATED IN MEMPHIS, TENNESSEE, TWO OF WHICH ARE OWNED AND THREE ARE LEASED. NIKE BRAND APPAREL AND EQUIPMENT PRODUCTS ARE ALSO SHIPPED FROM OUR LEASED FOOTHILL RANCH, CALIFORNIA DISTRIBUTION CENTER. CONVERSE AND HURLEY PRODUCTS ARE SHIPPED PRIMARILY FROM LEASED FACILITIES IN ONTARIO, CALIFORNIA. SMALLER LEASED DISTRIBUTION FACILITIES ARE LOCATED IN VARIOUS PARTS OF THE UNITED STATES.

