COUNTRIES. WE DO NOT OWN OR OPERATE ANY OF OUR OWN FOOTWEAR MANUFACTURING FACILITIES AND DEPEND UPON INDEPENDENT CONTRACT MANUFACTURERS TO MANUFACTURE ALL OF THE FOOTWEAR PRODUCTS WE SELL. IN FISCAL

