RECENTLY ADOPTED ACCOUNTING STANDARDS

IN NOVEMBER 2015, THE FASB ISSUED ASU NO. 2015-17,

INCOME TAXES (TOPIC 740): BALANCE SHEET CLASSIFICATION OF DEFERRED TAXES

TO SIMPLIFY THE PRESENTATION OF DEFERRED TAXES IN THE STATEMENT OF FINANCIAL POSITION. THE UPDATED GUIDANCE REQUIRES THAT DEFERRED TAX ASSETS AND LIABILITIES BE CLASSIFIED AS NON-CURRENT IN A CLASSIFIED BALANCE SHEET. THE COMPANY ELECTED TO EARLY ADOPT ASU 2015-17 ON A RETROSPECTIVE BASIS IN THE FOURTH QUARTER OF FISCAL 2016. THE ADOPTION OF THIS STANDARD REDUCED

